abstract: After coding your amazing Flask app, now you have to deploy and operate it. Kubernetes is a great way to do this, but it isn't easy to get started with creating a container and knowing what your deployment options are. In this talk we look at a few options so that the next time you have to deploy your Flask application you know which option is best for you!
